00:03:51.200 --> 00:03:54.090
So if you found a mirror plane
and a glide plane is an

00:03:54.090 --> 00:03:56.800
independent symmetry plane,
when is it MG,

00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:59.070
and when is it GM?

00:03:59.070 --> 00:04:02.790
