00:04:13.650 --> 00:04:18.320
P 4 GM, P 4 general manager.

00:04:18.320 --> 00:04:20.910
Now that is--

00:04:20.910 --> 00:04:22.690
hey, it works for me.

00:04:22.690 --> 00:04:26.750
But another way of saying it
